Class ComplexCondition

  • java.lang.Object

    Condition

    public final class ComplexCondition
extends java.lang.Object
implements Condition
    Complex condition made up of a collection of sub-conditions connected with a logical operator (AND, OR).

    Pierre Lison (plison@ifi.uio.no)

      • isSatisfiedBy

        public boolean isSatisfiedBy(Assignment input)
        Returns true if the complex condition is satisfied by the input assignment, and false otherwise.

        If the logical operator is AND, all the subconditions must be satisfied. If the operator is OR, at least one must be satisfied.

        Specified by:
        isSatisfiedBy in interface Condition
        Parameters:
